      <title>MultiPlan 因达成 45 亿美元再融资协议而飙升 82%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/multiplan-inks-deal-with-creditors-to-refinance-4-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份声明显示，医疗分析公司 MultiPlan Corp. 已与大多数债权人达成协议，延长其现有债务的到期日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/multiplan-inks-deal-with-creditors-to-refinance-4-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 13:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股市为 2024 年上涨做最后冲刺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/emerging-market-assets-advance-in-final-push-for-2024-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市周二上涨，在亚洲科技股上涨和中国准备推出更多刺激措施的迹象的推动下，主要股市指数有望以近两位数的回报率结束今年的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/emerging-market-assets-advance-in-final-push-for-2024-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 10:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克当选总统希望在动乱后恢复投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任总统丹尼尔·查波计划举行民族和解谈判，以解决不断升级的政治危机，该危机已导致数十人死亡，并导致这个天然气资源丰富的国家经济增长停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-24/president-elect-chapo-plans-dialog-to-end-mozambique-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 09:09:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
